                'description' => '<p><b>Martin Buber</b> (Hebrew: <span dir="rtl">מרטין בובר</span>‬; German: <i><span lang="de">Martin Buber</span></i>; Yiddish: <span lang="yi" dir="rtl">מארטין בובער</span>‎; February 8, 1878 –
